00:18:26,021 --> 00:18:27,106
- Mari sini. 
- Ya.

245
00:18:29,108 --> 00:18:29,942
Baiklah.

246
00:18:30,442 --> 00:18:33,904
Untuk memberi semangat kepada kamu 
untuk bertanding,

247
00:18:33,987 --> 00:18:36,990
saya tempah penginapan di tepi laut.

248
00:18:37,074 --> 00:18:38,951
Jadi apa patut kamu buat sekarang?

249
00:18:39,034 --> 00:18:40,285
- Buat yang… 
- Ya.

250
00:18:40,369 --> 00:18:42,538
Kamu mesti buat yang terbaik. Faham?

251
00:18:42,621 --> 00:18:44,373
- Ya. 
- Bagus.

252
00:18:44,456 --> 00:18:47,459
Pergi ke bilik kamu 
dan timbang berat dulu.

253
00:18:47,543 --> 00:18:49,419
Kalau hampir dengan had berat,

254
00:18:49,503 --> 00:18:52,422
jangan makan apa-apa 
sebelum kejohanan. Faham?

255
00:18:52,506 --> 00:18:53,882
- En. Park. 
- Ya?

256
00:18:53,966 --> 00:18:55,342
Mana Kim Baek-du?

257
00:18:55,425 --> 00:18:56,301
Apa?

258
00:18:57,970 --> 00:18:58,804
Apa?

259
00:18:59,638 --> 00:19:01,181
Dia pergi ke mana?

260
00:19:01,723 --> 00:19:02,641
- Baek-du? 
- Dia…

261
00:19:02,724 --> 00:19:06,562
Kami sangka dia tak bertanding. 
Jadi kami tak tunggu dia.

262
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:12,526
Ada banyak panggilan tak berjawab.

263
00:19:13,235 --> 00:19:14,069
Biar saya lihat.

264
00:19:14,153 --> 00:19:15,237
Aduhai.

265
00:19:15,779 --> 00:19:18,782
Kenapa polis peronda itu sibuk 
nak ambil keterangan

266
00:19:18,866 --> 00:19:21,451
kedua-dua pihak? Buang masa betul.

267
00:19:22,161 --> 00:19:25,122
Dia ingat dia Solomon? Saya dah lambatlah.

268
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:29,168
Wah, cantiknya…

269
00:19:29,251 --> 00:19:30,752
Awak seronok?

270
00:19:30,836 --> 00:19:32,754
Siap boleh menyanyi lagi?

271
00:19:32,838 --> 00:19:34,756
Hei, Du-sik.

272
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:39,052
Apa kata kita bertolak awal lain kali 
dan lalu jalan ini?

273
00:19:39,136 --> 00:19:41,138
Jalan ini lebih jauh,

274
00:19:41,221 --> 00:19:43,932
tapi pemandangannya cantik 
sepanjang tahun.

275
00:19:44,016 --> 00:19:46,435
Awak nak saya sembam muka awak ke tanah?

276
00:19:46,518 --> 00:19:49,229
Kalau awak ketinggalan bas lagi,

277
00:19:49,313 --> 00:19:50,898
siap awak.

278
00:19:50,981 --> 00:19:52,274
- Faham? 
- Oh, ya!

279
00:19:52,357 --> 00:19:55,694
Kita mesti singgah di hentian rehat. 
Jangan lupa.

280
00:19:56,361 --> 00:19:58,238
Diamlah!

281
00:19:58,322 --> 00:20:00,782
- Apa? 
- Apa masalah awak?

282
00:20:01,408 --> 00:20:03,118
Cantiknya tempat ini.

283
00:20:03,202 --> 00:20:04,536
Aduhai.

284
00:20:04,620 --> 00:20:07,539
Awak tak habis-habis buat hal.

285
00:20:08,123 --> 00:20:11,001
Hai, Putih. Tentu awak dahaga.

286
00:20:11,084 --> 00:20:14,171
Awak tak ada kerja lainkah?

287
00:20:14,254 --> 00:20:17,216
Awak melepak dengan anjing waktu bertugas?

288
00:20:17,299 --> 00:20:20,010
Saya bukannya melepak dengan Putih.

289
00:20:20,093 --> 00:20:23,430
Kalau nak melepak, 
saya lepak dengan Baek-du atau Jin-su.

290
00:20:23,513 --> 00:20:25,098
Bukan dengan anjing.

291
00:20:25,182 --> 00:20:28,310
Awak pasti? 
Saya rasa awak dan Putih tak jauh beza.

292
00:20:28,810 --> 00:20:29,811
Mana ada!

293
00:20:29,895 --> 00:20:33,649
Ini semua salah awak, Putih. 
Jangan lari lagi!

294
00:20:33,732 --> 00:20:35,150
Aduhai.

295
00:20:35,234 --> 00:20:36,860
Anjing itu lari lagi?

296
00:20:37,486 --> 00:20:38,445
Hari ini ke mana?

297
00:20:38,528 --> 00:20:42,574
Ia cuba lari ke takungan air lagi, 
tapi saya sempat tangkap.

298
00:20:42,658 --> 00:20:46,411
Tentu ada sebab ia asyik ke takungan air.

299
00:20:48,247 --> 00:20:49,414
Hei, Lee Gyeong-mun!

300
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:58,006
Awak dari mana?

301
00:20:58,548 --> 00:21:00,926
Saya suruh awak jaga kedai sekejap.

302
00:21:01,009 --> 00:21:03,095
Itu pun awak tak boleh buat?

303
00:21:04,054 --> 00:21:06,348
Kenapa awak asyik merayau-rayau?

304
00:21:06,431 --> 00:21:08,767
Kaki gatal sangat? Tak boleh duduk diam?

305
00:21:08,850 --> 00:21:09,685
- Saya… 
- Awak.

306
00:21:10,269 --> 00:21:13,480
Kalau nak keluar, beritahulah saya dulu.

307
00:21:13,563 --> 00:21:15,691
Ada banyak kuih beras di gerai.

308
00:21:15,774 --> 00:21:18,402
Senang-senang saja orang boleh curi!

309
00:21:18,485 --> 00:21:19,528
Awak dah gilakah?

310
00:21:19,611 --> 00:21:21,363
Putih pun ada.

311
00:21:22,698 --> 00:21:25,325
- Putih. 
- Lee Gyeong-mun. Hei!

312
00:21:25,826 --> 00:21:29,621
Awak tak nampakkah? 
Putih cakap jangan bergaduh lagi.

313
00:21:29,705 --> 00:21:31,707
Gandhi, awak pencinta damai, bukan?

314
00:21:32,457 --> 00:21:35,752
Dalam perjalanan ke sini tadi, 
saya nampak kafe tutup.

315
00:21:35,836 --> 00:21:38,130
Kafe mana? Kafe Mi-ran?

316
00:21:38,213 --> 00:21:41,675
Dia buka dan tutup kedai

317
00:21:41,758 --> 00:21:43,510
sesuka hatinya.

318
00:21:43,593 --> 00:21:45,137
Dia tak takut rugi pun.

319
00:21:45,762 --> 00:21:47,806
Yakah? Tapi tak apakah?

320
00:21:47,889 --> 00:21:50,684
Terpulang kepada dialah. Itu kafe dia.

321
00:21:52,477 --> 00:21:53,812
Yakah?

322
00:21:54,730 --> 00:21:58,442
HENTIAN REHAT NAMHANG

323
00:22:02,321 --> 00:22:05,574
Kenapa lama sangat?

324
00:22:10,954 --> 00:22:11,955
Du-sik!

325
00:22:15,042 --> 00:22:17,919
Dia ingat kami nak pergi berkelah?

326
00:22:19,629 --> 00:22:23,050
Nanti perlu timbang berat, bukan? 
Kenapa makan banyak sangat?

327
00:22:23,133 --> 00:22:25,385
Saya makan banyak pun, 
berat saya tak naik.

328
00:22:25,469 --> 00:22:26,345
SELAMAT DATANG

329
00:22:27,304 --> 00:22:30,974
Kim Baek-du, 81 perpuluhan…

330
00:22:32,100 --> 00:22:32,934
dua?

331
00:22:33,685 --> 00:22:34,728
Apa? Macam mana…

332
00:22:35,437 --> 00:22:37,773
Hei, Kim Baek-du.

333
00:22:37,856 --> 00:22:39,733
Kenapa berat awak naik?

334
00:22:39,816 --> 00:22:40,984
Silap rasanya.

335
00:22:41,068 --> 00:22:44,071
Semalam berat saya 79.7 kg. 
Penimbang ini tak betul.

336
00:22:44,154 --> 00:22:47,324
Jadi macam mana berat awak 
boleh naik 1 kg sehari?

337
00:22:47,407 --> 00:22:48,992
- Peliknya. 
- Awak…

338
00:22:49,743 --> 00:22:50,994
Awak makan apa hari ini?

339
00:22:51,078 --> 00:22:51,912
Hari ini?

340
00:22:52,496 --> 00:22:55,791
Tak banyak pun. Sarapan dan…

341
00:22:56,291 --> 00:22:59,211
Oh, ya. Saya makan di hentian rehat.

342
00:23:00,003 --> 00:23:01,838
Biskut walnut dan sate ikan.

343
00:23:02,506 --> 00:23:05,550
Oh, ya. Dan beberapa biji kentang kecil…

344
00:23:05,634 --> 00:23:07,552
Kentang kecil?

345
00:23:07,636 --> 00:23:10,680
Awak gila? Kenapa makan banyak 
sebelum timbang berat?

346
00:23:10,764 --> 00:23:13,183
Berat saya tak naik walaupun makan banyak.

347
00:23:13,266 --> 00:23:16,478
Awak yang beria-ia nak bertanding! 
Awak dah gilakah?

348
00:23:17,395 --> 00:23:20,440
Jangan tercegat saja. 
Pakai baju tebal dan pergi lari!

349
00:23:23,318 --> 00:23:24,736
Cepat.

350
00:23:33,161 --> 00:23:35,580
Jangan berjalan! Lari!

351
00:23:38,458 --> 00:23:39,417
Jeong-hun!

352
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:47,175
Maaflah menyusahkan awak pula. 
Tentu awak banyak kerja.

353
00:23:47,259 --> 00:23:49,177
Tak apa.

354
00:23:49,261 --> 00:23:50,762
Kalau bukan sebab awak,

355
00:23:50,846 --> 00:23:53,223
entah apalah nasib dia.

356
00:23:54,307 --> 00:23:55,934
Awak selamatkan nyawa dia.

357
00:23:56,017 --> 00:23:58,728
Aduhai, tak adalah sampai tahap itu.

358
00:24:00,939 --> 00:24:02,482
Tapi lebih baik

359
00:24:03,608 --> 00:24:06,319
kalau awak tak biar 
dia makan banyak sangat.

360
00:24:08,029 --> 00:24:08,905
Apa?

361
00:24:10,365 --> 00:24:11,283
Bukan apa.

362
00:24:11,867 --> 00:24:15,370
Sayanglah kalau dia tak layak 
bertanding kerana terlebih berat.

363
00:24:16,121 --> 00:24:17,581
Susah-susah kamu datang.

364
00:24:21,501 --> 00:24:22,836
Hei, Baek-du!

365
00:24:22,919 --> 00:24:25,505
Macam mana nak turun berat badan begitu?

366
00:24:26,965 --> 00:24:28,341
Hei!

367
00:24:29,092 --> 00:24:31,636
Lari sambil dukung kawan. 
Itu lebih berkesan!

368
00:24:32,721 --> 00:24:33,555
Dukung siapa?

369
00:24:35,098 --> 00:24:36,516
Boleh saya tolong dia?

370
00:24:38,602 --> 00:24:39,978
Tak payah.

371
00:24:40,061 --> 00:24:42,355
Patah pula pinggang dia nanti.

372
00:24:42,898 --> 00:24:43,732
Pergi.

373
00:24:44,941 --> 00:24:47,903
Apa nak buat? Timbang berat tak lama lagi.

374
00:24:48,945 --> 00:24:52,657
Kalau nak turun 1.4 kg, 
dia patut dukung seseorang…

375
00:25:00,123 --> 00:25:03,752
Kenapa kamu semua pandang saya begitu?

376
00:25:05,837 --> 00:25:09,549
Hei, saya berat sangatkah?

377
00:25:11,468 --> 00:25:13,136
Jangan main-main.

378
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:15,805
Saya tak berat sangatlah.

379
00:25:15,889 --> 00:25:17,390
- Du-sik. 
- Biar betul.

380
00:25:17,474 --> 00:25:20,143
Du-sik.

381
00:25:20,227 --> 00:25:24,231
Saya boleh rasa darah di tekak saya.

382
00:25:25,273 --> 00:25:28,109
Tapi awak nampaknya cukup makan

383
00:25:28,193 --> 00:25:30,528
sepanjang 20 tahun lepas,

384
00:25:30,612 --> 00:25:31,821
jadi saya tak kisah.

385
00:25:33,782 --> 00:25:35,825
Hei, turunkan saya.

386
00:25:35,909 --> 00:25:37,327
- Hei. 
- Turunkan saya.

387
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:38,912
- Jangan bergerak. 
- Saya…

388
00:25:38,995 --> 00:25:39,955
Saya penatlah!

389
00:25:40,080 --> 00:25:41,414
Jangan bergerak.

390
00:25:41,498 --> 00:25:43,500
Awak memang nak kena.

391
00:25:47,254 --> 00:25:48,546
- Hei! 
- Tunggu.

392
00:25:48,630 --> 00:25:50,715
Saya hampir jatuh! Pegang kuat-kuat!

393
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:53,385
- Tangan awak! 
- Okey.

394
00:25:53,468 --> 00:25:54,594
- Aduh. 
- Teruk betul.

395
00:25:56,763 --> 00:25:58,640
Pasukan Geosan-gun, Kim Baek-du.

396
00:25:58,723 --> 00:25:59,599
Ya.

397
00:25:59,683 --> 00:26:00,725
- Baek-du. 
- Ya?

398
00:26:20,036 --> 00:26:21,496
Turunkan ibu jari kaki.

399
00:26:29,379 --> 00:26:30,213
Lepas.

400
00:26:34,342 --> 00:26:35,176
Saya lepas!

401
00:26:37,554 --> 00:26:39,222
Ya Tuhan.

402
00:26:39,306 --> 00:26:41,016
Saya nyaris tersingkir!

403
00:26:42,392 --> 00:26:43,268
Ya!

404
00:26:44,144 --> 00:26:45,979
Boleh beri dua gelas?

405
00:26:46,062 --> 00:26:47,605
Terima kasih.

406
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,941
Saya punya, jangan makan.

407
00:26:50,025 --> 00:26:51,151
Aduhai.

408
00:26:51,234 --> 00:26:52,444
Baek-du.

409
00:26:52,527 --> 00:26:54,779
Berat awak pun naik kalau makan banyak.

410
00:26:54,863 --> 00:26:57,282
Berat semua orang naik kalau makan banyak.

411
00:26:57,365 --> 00:27:00,702
Saya betul-betul lapar 
sebab lama bersenam tadi.

412
00:27:00,785 --> 00:27:02,412
Makanlah puas-puas.

413
00:27:02,495 --> 00:27:04,748
- Awak jangan makan lagi. 
- Baik.

414
00:27:04,831 --> 00:27:06,458
- Makanlah. 
- Baik!

415
00:27:06,541 --> 00:27:07,667
Mak cik.

416
00:27:08,209 --> 00:27:11,546
Ada makanan lain selain makanan laut?

417
00:27:11,629 --> 00:27:14,632
Ini restoran sashimi. 
Kenapa minta makanan lain?

418
00:27:15,258 --> 00:27:16,843
Hari ini nak tukar selera.

419
00:27:17,927 --> 00:27:18,762
Kenapa?

420
00:27:18,845 --> 00:27:21,431
Awak kata awak boleh makan 
sashimi setiap hari.

421
00:27:21,514 --> 00:27:23,266
Kalau tak nak, biar saya makan.

422
00:27:23,350 --> 00:27:24,851
Ya, awak makanlah.

423
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,897
Jangan ambil banyak sangat.

424
00:27:31,733 --> 00:27:33,234
Ada banyak lagilah.

425
00:27:33,318 --> 00:27:34,736
Ini untuk kamu berdua?

426
00:27:43,370 --> 00:27:44,245
Ya.

427
00:27:47,123 --> 00:27:47,957
Di mana?

428
00:27:48,041 --> 00:27:50,043
Telefon awam di pasar?

429
00:27:50,585 --> 00:27:52,379
Ada enam panggilan dari sana.

430
00:27:52,879 --> 00:27:55,882
Kami semak semua panggilan Yeon 
sejak tiga bulan lepas

431
00:27:55,965 --> 00:27:57,425
kecuali enam panggilan itu.

432
00:27:57,509 --> 00:27:59,886
UNIT SIASATAN 3

433
00:27:59,969 --> 00:28:02,764
Tidak, bukan Choi Chil-seong.

434
00:28:02,847 --> 00:28:05,809
Dia pun dapat panggilan dari sana 
selepas Choi mati.

435
00:28:07,018 --> 00:28:09,938
Saya rasa ada orang tengah

436
00:28:10,021 --> 00:28:12,732
antara Choi Chil-seong 
dan Yeon Sang-cheol.

437
00:28:14,651 --> 00:28:15,485
Hei.

438
00:28:16,236 --> 00:28:17,654
Awak di mana sekarang?

439
00:28:18,822 --> 00:28:19,656
Namhang?

440
00:28:22,325 --> 00:28:26,079
Saya suruh jadi pengintip, 
bukan pergi bercuti.

441
00:28:26,579 --> 00:28:27,747
Sudahlah.

442
00:28:27,831 --> 00:28:29,416
Jangan buang masa lagi.

443
00:28:29,499 --> 00:28:31,543
Saya dah cakap kita tak ada masa.

444
00:28:32,210 --> 00:28:33,253
Tunggu, puan.

445
00:28:34,337 --> 00:28:35,171
Apa?

446
00:28:35,255 --> 00:28:38,675
Yang saya minta tolong dulu…

447
00:28:39,634 --> 00:28:41,136
belum selesai, ya?

448
00:28:41,719 --> 00:28:42,762
Hei.

449
00:28:42,846 --> 00:28:45,390
Awak pun tahu dokumen rasmi memang lambat.

450
00:28:45,974 --> 00:28:48,435
Tunggu saja. Beberapa hari lagi siaplah.

451
00:28:50,395 --> 00:28:51,229
Okey.

452
00:28:54,232 --> 00:28:55,525
Baiklah.

453
00:28:56,568 --> 00:28:57,527
Okey.

454
00:29:06,161 --> 00:29:08,246
Hei, awak buat apa di sini?

455
00:29:08,788 --> 00:29:10,874
Tak ada apa-apa.

456
00:29:10,957 --> 00:29:11,791
Kenapa?

457
00:29:12,751 --> 00:29:14,711
Tak banyak makanan di sini, ya?

458
00:29:15,837 --> 00:29:18,423
Tak apa, saya dah makan sikit. Awak?

459
00:29:18,506 --> 00:29:20,759
Awak buat apa di sini?

460
00:29:20,842 --> 00:29:24,345
Awak patut makan banyak 
untuk perlawanan esok.

461
00:29:24,429 --> 00:29:27,056
Tak apa. Saya tak lapar sangat.

462
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:29,809
Kalau lapar nanti, 
saya boleh buat mi segera.

463
00:29:33,271 --> 00:29:34,230
Nak lepak…

464
00:29:36,441 --> 00:29:37,484
di bilik saya nanti?

465
00:29:38,193 --> 00:29:39,027
Apa?

466
00:29:40,779 --> 00:29:41,613
Nak buat apa?

467
00:29:42,322 --> 00:29:43,615
Borak sambil makan mi.

468
00:29:44,407 --> 00:29:45,241
Nak tak?

469
00:29:52,832 --> 00:29:53,958
Awak…

470
00:29:54,042 --> 00:29:57,253
Awak nak buat apa?

471
00:29:57,337 --> 00:29:58,880
Apa pula kali ini?

472
00:29:58,963 --> 00:30:03,009
Awak biar betul. 
Awak ajak saya melepak di bilik awak?

473
00:30:03,092 --> 00:30:04,302
Dan makan mi?

474
00:30:04,385 --> 00:30:07,013
- Dasar otak kuning. 
- Hei.

475
00:30:07,096 --> 00:30:09,057
Keji betul!

476
00:30:09,140 --> 00:30:10,266
Apa yang awak fikir?

477
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,893
Dari mana awak belajar?

478
00:30:11,976 --> 00:30:13,770
Hei, apa maksud awak?

479
00:30:13,853 --> 00:30:15,730
Saya ajak makan mi segera.

480
00:30:15,814 --> 00:30:17,357
Makan lewat malam.

481
00:30:17,899 --> 00:30:20,109
Awak makan sikit saja di sini,

482
00:30:20,193 --> 00:30:21,986
jadi tentu awak lapar nanti.

483
00:30:22,070 --> 00:30:23,947
Jadi saya nak buat mi untuk awak.

484
00:30:25,073 --> 00:30:26,950
Tiba-tiba kena pukul.

485
00:30:27,575 --> 00:30:28,576
